{"tid":1738733,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"施恩莫望報，慈善機構只係收捐款有咩好話？","createTime":"2019-11-19T10:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T13:46:30.000Z","uid":102240,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4687abd0dc69bc17504332d834f6f4068e0bbc95","tid":1738733,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"唔捐就唔捐，無必要話人"},{"pid":"aec8c7ac870f45f2a32c3ff923fd2e9d77f22ec2","tid":1738733,"uid":327316,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"4687abd0dc69bc17504332d834f6f4068e0bbc95","tid":1738733,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"唔捐就唔捐，無必要話人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"捐錢比佢係要支持佢救人。先不論係咪出現響香港，有人道災難而選擇唔救，已違背佢組織宗旨。佢繼續打住呢個旗號收人捐嘅錢，你覺得無問題？"},{"pid":"f788961175752022789f25a020c8acd919a052de","tid":1738733,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"咁左膠鍾意企道德高地講普世價值"},{"pid":"27a97873d9d35dbbbc3893e35aa0fd2354c33378","tid":1738733,"uid":161935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4687abd0dc69bc17504332d834f6f4068e0bbc95","tid":1738733,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"唔捐就唔捐，無必要話人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"望都望唔使佢幫。<br />\n問題係香港的確出現左人道災難，無論有無捐錢比佢，都需要佢嘅出現。<br />\n偏偏佢平時收捐款果時咁誠懇，同佢拒絕提供援助果陣，個嘴臉相差幾大？<br />\n比人當水魚咁㩒，邊個唔嬲？"},{"pid":"6edc78ab3b083c029a0f32a9852203548bde9890","tid":1738733,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"博負評？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ca2d6d7a6c96442c9fda71ec9548928ea03cfc","tid":1738733,"uid":40292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6edc78ab3b083c029a0f32a9852203548bde9890","tid":1738733,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"博負評？<img src=\"/ass